xt4";s:0:"";s:20:"parabola_sliderlink4";s:0:"";s:19:"parabola_sliderimg5";s:0:"";s:21:"parabola_slidertitle5";s:0:"";s:20:"parabola_slidertext5";s:0:"";s:20:"parabola_sliderlink5";s:0:"";s:18:"parabola_nrcolumns";s:1:"3";s:23:"parabola_colimageheight";i:201;s:23:"parabola_columnreadmore";s:9:"Read more";s:19:"parabola_columnimg1";s:86:"http://localhost/wc2014/wp-content/themes/parabola/images/columns/parabola-column1.jpg";s:21:"parabola_columntitle1";s:21:"Hi there I''m a title!";s:20:"parabola_columntext1";s:127:"You can also have some text here. Just like with the slider, everything is optional (including the title and the link inputs). ";s:20:"parabola_columnlink1";s:29:"http://www.cryoutcreations.eu";s:19:"parabola_columnimg2";s:86:"http://localhost/wc2014/wp-content/themes/parabola/images/columns/parabola-column2.jpg";s:21:"parabola_columntitle2";s:21:"You can use HTML tags";s:20:"parabola_columntext2";s:173:"You can also use <a href=''http://www.cryoutcreations.eu''>links</a> as well as most <strong>other</strong> <u>HTML</u> <em>tags</em> and even [shortcodes] inside the columns.";s:20:"parabola_columnlink2";s:29:"http://www.cryoutcreations.eu";s:19:"parabola_columnimg3";s:86:"http://localhost/wc2014/wp-content/themes/parabola/images/columns/parabola-column3.jpg";s:21:"parabola_columntitle3";s:25:"Just another column title";s:20:"parabola_columntext3";s:103:"You can have up to four columns or choose to have no columns at all. It''s all up to you and your needs.";s:20:"parabola_columnlink3";s:29:"http://www.cryoutcreations.eu";s:19:"parabola_columnimg4";s:0:"";s:21:"parabola_columntitle4";s:0:"";s:20:"parabola_columntext4";s:0:"";s:20:"parabola_columnlink4";s:0:"";s:19:"parabola_fronttext1";s:0:"";s:19:"parabola_fronttext2";s:0:"";s:19:"parabola_fronttext3";s:495:"And underneath the columns you can have 2 more text boxes that also support <em>HTML tags</em> and [shortcodes]. You can also choose to have just one text area or none. Deleting all\r\n						text inside the appropriate input in the Parabola Settings will remove this whole text area.<br /> As you can see it''s really all up to you. You are free to do whatever you like. <br>\r\n						<strong>It''s a multi-universe of options and you are only limited by your (and our) imagination! Have fun!</strong>";s:19:"parabola_fronttext4";s:0:"";s:24:"parabola_fronthideheader";s:0:"";s:22:"parabola_fronthidemenu";s:0:"";s:24:"parabola_fronthidewidget";s:0:"";s:24:"parabola_fronthidefooter";s:0:"";s:22:"parabola_fronthideback";s:0:"";s:16:"parabola_hheight";i:120;s:16:"parabola_hcenter";i:0;s:15:"parabola_hratio";i:0;s:19:"parabola_logoupload";s:0:"";s:16:"parabola_favicon";s:0:"";s:19:"parabola_siteheader";s:26:"Site Title and Description";s:24:"parabola_headermargintop";i:40;s:25:"parabola_headermarginleft";i:0;s:19:"parabola_fontfamily";s:9:"Open Sans";s:19:"parabola_googlefont";s:0:"";s:17:"parabola_fontsize";s:4:"14px";s:18:"parabola_fonttitle";s:10:"Bebas Neue";s:24:"parabola_googlefonttitle";s:0:"";s:21:"parabola_headfontsize";s:4:"34px";s:17:"parabola_fontside";s:10:"Bebas Neue";s:23:"parabola_googlefontside";s:0:"";s:21:"parabola_sidefontsize";s:4:"18px";s:22:"parabola_sitetitlefont";s:14:"Oswald Stencil";s:28:"parabola_sitetitlegooglefont";s:0:"";s:22:"parabola_sitetitlesize";s:4:"38px";s:17:"parabola_menufont";s:9:"Open Sans";s:23:"parabola_menugooglefont";s:0:"";s:21:"parabola_menufontsize";s:4:"14px";s:21:"parabola_headingsfont";s:25:"Yanone Kaffeesatz Regular";s:27:"parabola_headingsgooglefont";s:0:"";s:25:"parabola_headingsfontsize";s:4:"120%";s:18:"parabola_textalign";s:7:"Default";s:23:"parabola_paragraphspace";s:5:"1.0em";s:18:"parabola_parindent";s:3:"0px";s:23:"parabola_headingsindent";s:7:"Disable";s:19:"parabola_lineheight";s:5:"1.7em";s:18:"parabola_wordspace";s:7:"Default";s:20:"parabola_letterspace";s:7:"Default";s:22:"parabola_uppercasetext";s:1:"1";s:21:"parabola_colorschemes";s:14:"Parabola Light";s:24:"parabola_backcolorheader";s:7:"#0e0e0e";s:22:"